OL,3,CWest Ham appoint new manager after
OL,4,Csacking Julen Lopetegui
OL,6,FGraham Potter has been announced as
OL,7,FWest Ham new manager after the team
OL,8,Fsacked head coach Julen Lopetegui
OL,9,Fafter less than eight months in charge.
OL,11,FThe former Brighton and Chelsea boss
OL,12,FGraham Potter has signed a two-and-a-
OL,13,Fhalf-year contract with The Hammers.
OL,15,FIn a press conference this morning,
OL,16,Fthe new boss said he's "very excited
OL,17,Fand proud to be in charge of this
OL,18,Famazing Club.
