OL,6,F"It's a bit like Christmas for adults!
OL,7,FI didn't sleep much last night because
OL,8,Fof the excitement. I can't wait to
OL,9,Fmeet everyone and get going."
OL,11,FThe new manager was asked about his
OL,12,Fambitions for the club. He said:
OL,13,F"There's tradition and demands here,
OL,14,Fand recent success. That's what we
OL,15,Fwant to work towards.
OL,17,F"It's my first day, so I need to meet
OL,18,Feveryone, and tomorrow's match will be
OL,19,Fmy immediate focus.
