OL,6,F"I think if you can create a team that
OL,7,Fthe fans identify with, and get
OL,8,Feveryone aligned with what we want to
OL,9,Fachieve, and build trust, that's key."
OL,11,FIn a statement on Wednesday West Ham
OL,12,FUnited confirmed head coach Julen
OL,13,FLopetegui left the club.
OL,15,FThe statement read: "The first half of
OL,16,Fthe 2024/25 season has not aligned
OL,17,Fwith the club's ambitions and the club
OL,18,Fhas therefore taken action in line
OL,19,Fwith its objectives.
