OL,3,CWest Ham appoint new manager after
OL,4,Csacking Julen Lopetegui
OL,6,FThe 58-year-old was appointed in May
OL,7,Fto replace David Moyes, who left the
OL,8,Fclub at the end of last season after
OL,9,Fhis contract expired.
OL,11,FHe was tasked with bringing a more
OL,12,Fattacking style of play to the London
OL,13,FStadium after some fans grew
OL,14,Ffrustrated with Moyes' pragmatic
OL,15,Fapproach, even though the Scot led the
OL,16,Fclub to a first trophy in 43 years
OL,17,Fwhen they won the Europa Conference
OL,18,FLeague in 2023.
