OL,6,FBut despite a #130million spending
OL,7,Fspree in the summer, bringing in nine
OL,8,Fplayers including Germany striker
OL,9,FNiclas Fullkrug and Wolves captain Max
OL,10,FKilman, results have been poor with
OL,11,FWest Ham a lowly 14th in the Premier
OL,12,FLeague.
OL,14,FLopetegui's position was under threat
OL,15,Fin early December following a 3-1
OL,16,Fdefeat at Leicester, but a run of four
OL,17,Fmatches unbeaten earned him a stay of
OL,18,Fexecution.
