OL,6,FHowever, the manner of the 5-0 home
OL,7,Fdefeat by Liverpool after Christmas,
OL,8,Ffollowed by a 4-1 loss at Manchester
OL,9,FCity on Saturday, set alarms bells
OL,10,Fringing again among the West Ham
OL,11,Fhierarchy.
OL,13,FTechnical director Tim Steidten, who
OL,14,Fis understood to have advocated
OL,15,Fappointing Potter in the summer, has
OL,16,Fbeen staying away from the training
OL,17,Fground amid reports of tension between
OL,18,Fhim and Lopetegui.
