OL,3,CWest Ham appoint new manager after
OL,4,Csacking Julen Lopetegui
OL,6,FWest Ham say the German, 45, is
OL,7,Ffocusing on the January transfer
OL,8,Fwindow, which opened last week.
OL,10,FThe club are looking at potential
OL,11,Fstriking options with Jarrod Bowen out
OL,12,Ffor six weeks with a fractured foot
OL,13,Fand Michail Antonio facing a long road
OL,14,Fback after he was injured in a car
OL,15,Faccident last month.
OL,17,FPotter returns to management 20 months
OL,18,Fsince he was sacked by Chelsea just
OL,19,Fseven months and 31 matches into a
OL,20,Ffive-year contract.
